description.plain:
This is the lead single off of JGRREY’s soon to be released EP, Grreydaze on March 8th 2019.
The Grreydaze – EP will be her first project.
In an interview she says,  “I wanted to show how freely my mind wonders, how many times I’m unsure of whether something has happened or if it was a daydream, that fine line between a memory and a dream…”
